 sans-serif; color: rgb(75, 79, 86); font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: normal;\"><br><br>About the place:&nbsp;<br>Akshi beach is one of the most sought after beaches of the many beaches in Alibaug. It\'s a 3hr drive away from Mumbai city.&nbsp;<br>Album link :&nbsp;<a href=\"https://goo.gl/photos/GS2NaGBtKmTom2cZ6\" rel=\"noopener nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" data-lynx-mode=\"async\" data-lynx-uri=\"https://l.facebook.com/l.php?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2Fphotos%2FGS2NaGBtKmTom2cZ6&amp;h=ATOSZo9eAPn_N_8xapXo1Bb1jEk19KHbvGwrqrN_ZSHXN3x0DSmatKWScauBNoyMP6upqMimHihN6fA3d6vB-IwoLhB5G0aalCq01FvdiW7-YUxu0IqakCzTjr0JpTBR0RNtnYVw66NOBNSAWahotafKbaH6LaLlJiM7Yv3drlz8sZS_\" style=\"color: rgb(54, 88, 153); cursor: pointer; font-family: inherit;\"><span style=\"font-family: inherit;\">https://goo.gl/photos/</span><wbr><span class=\"word_break\" style=\"display: inline-block; font-family: inherit;\"></span>GS2NaGBtKmTom2cZ6</a><br><br>Plan:<br>Day 1 (Saturday) - The long ride begins!<br><br>Reach campsite by 4pm where Team Mapping Journeys would be waiting to embrace your arrival :D<br>Settle in your the tents and grab onto some snacks.<br>The beach is just a few steps away from the site, so after snacks, head to the beach and spend the evening with the setting sun.<br>A beachside camping is incomplete without local homemade delicacies. Home-cooked dinner served.&nbsp;<br>Post dinner, the campfire and light music will be up -- a perfect setting for sharing your thoughts and stories.<br><br>Day 2 (Sunday) - Sunrise at the beach!<br><br>The wake up call will be at 6am (for those who do not want to miss the sunrise).<br>Breakfast will be served on your return from the beach.<br>The check out time will be 11am.&nbsp;<br><br>Cost : 2100?/- per person. (Group discount applicable for 3 or more people.)<br><br>For payment using credit/debit card/net-banking :<br><a href=\"https://l.facebook.com/l.php?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FkdLpHk&amp;h=ATNL0al4QhPhPCsuxQcvnD1uqtj4qtx-CYWvTbzLAzVa8AaoXplw