: normal;\"><br>Two hours from Mumbai, the Moksh Mantra campsite is located in Varsai area off Khopoli- Pen road. Nestled among hills, with acres of green plains spread around and a view of the mighty Manikgad, it is a site for a comfortable yet raw camping experience. With no unwanted vehicle sound it is the perfect excuse to reconnect with your travel-buddies and yourself!&nbsp;<br><br>Campsite Photo Link :&nbsp;<a href=\"https://l.facebook.com/l.php?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2Fphotos%2FFqrpzZhcSscr75TU6&amp;h=ATMVZoGfZaHFLSCNHEBx0mWMq3SgR-i4dNOen3Wr35gCypxr6PKdeO33RNU-2QySblYZWKdbVS2IHJO9lrtf2S76_mXWlXnKIiTnCvZATA6zIekwiK8dtbxIMC4rIeekfU-obsLXmiQDoTHN9Zk2oaxw5G8SH9dS-flfvVBzDOT6bi6kEac\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\" data-lynx-mode=\"async\" style=\"color: rgb(54, 88, 153); font-family: inherit;\"><span style=\"font-family: inherit;\">https://goo.gl/photos/</span><wbr><span class=\"word_break\" style=\"display: inline-block; font-family: inherit;\"></span>FqrpzZhcSscr75TU6</a><br><br>Cost:Rs. 1400/- per person. (For people coming directly at the site)<br>Group discount applicable for 4 or more people.<br><br>Note:We can also club people interested in having a transport from Mumbai itself and arrange for a common bus starting from Dadar. (Give us a call to know about the cost)<br><br>Inclusions :<br>- Stay in tent(Couple/3/4 sharing), Sleeping bags (Dorm stay available)<br>- Meals: Evening snacks(Tea,pop corn,cold drinks,Samosa), Dinner (veg/non veg), Breakfast<br>- Movie screening<br>- Campfire<br>- Rain dance on day 2<br>- First aid and safety<br>- Campsite entry fees<br>- 4 Western style toilets, Activity area available at the campsite<br><br>Exclusions :<br>- Meals during travel.<br>- Personal expenses<br>- Insurance of any kind<br>- Medical hospitalization, evacuation and related expenses<br>- Any item not covered under “inclusions”<br><br>Smoking and consumption of alcohol is strictly prohibited around the tent and movie screening area. For confir