ial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: normal;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(29, 33, 41); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: normal;\">Till now almost every traveller knows the answer to the very simple question.</span><br style=\"color: rgb(29, 33, 41); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: normal;\"><br style=\"color: rgb(29, 33, 41); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: normal;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(29, 33, 41); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: normal;\">Why Kalsubai?</span><br style=\"color: rgb(29, 33, 41); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: normal;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(29, 33, 41); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: normal;\">Well, It\'s the highest peak of the state. Standing tall at 5400ft there is no other place in Maharashtra higher than this that you can reach. People come here to test their endurance/stamina and will power. There are fields to cross, ladders to climb and patience to test.</span><br style=\"color: rgb(29, 33, 41); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: normal;\"><br style=\"color: rgb(29, 33, 41); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: normal;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(29, 33, 41); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: normal;\">Wanna give it a try along with us?</span><br style=\"color: rgb(29, 33, 41); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: normal;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(29, 33, 41); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: normal;\">TAG ALONG :D</span><br style=\"color: rgb(29, 33, 41); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: normal;\"><br style=\"color: rgb(29, 33, 41); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: normal;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(29, 33, 41); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: normal;\"><b>About the terrain:</b> (All approximate data)</span><br style=\"color: rgb(29, 33, 41); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: normal;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(29, 33, 41); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: normal;\">Kalsubai has one of the highest ascent to be covered under a day/night(800mt), this is the elevation difference from Bari. To cover this vertical distance one needs to trek 5km in total which can be further segregated into,</span><br style=\"color: rgb(29, 33, 41); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: normal;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(29, 33, 41); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: normal;\">Flat/Climb/Descent: 0.9km/3.5km/0.8km</span><br style=\"color: rgb(29, 33, 41); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: normal;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(29, 33, 41); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: normal;\">This trek can be done even by first timers who lead a fitter lifestyle.</span><br style=\"color: rgb(29, 33, 41); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: normal;\"><br style=\"color: rgb(29, 33, 41); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: normal;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(29, 33, 41); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: normal;\"><b>Itinerary:</b></span><br style=\"color: rgb(29, 33, 41); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: normal;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(29, 33, 41); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: normal;\">Day 1 (Saturday)</span><br style=\"color: rgb(29, 33, 41); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: normal;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(29, 33, 41); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: normal;\">We all catch the Cst-Kasara local,</span><br style=\"color: rgb(29, 33, 41); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: normal;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(29, 33, 41); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: normal;\">Cstm 2.25pm - Dadar 2.38pm - Kurla 2.45pm - Ghatkopar 2.49pm - Thane 3.04pm - Dombivli 3.16pm - Kalyan 3.24pm - Kasara 4.34pm</span><br style=\"color: rgb(29, 33, 41); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: normal;\"><br style=\"color: rgb(29, 33, 41); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: normal;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(29, 33, 41); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: normal;\">Meeting point: Kasara ticket counter.</span><br style=\"color: rgb(29, 33, 41); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: normal;\"><br style=\"color: rgb(29, 33, 41); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: normal;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(29, 33, 41); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: normal;\">From Kasara we move towards the base village called Bari in local jeeps, the journey takes 2hrs.</span><br style=\"color: rgb(29, 33, 41); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: normal;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(29, 33, 41); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: normal;\">Once at the village hot tea and snacks will be served.</span><br style=\"color: rgb(29, 33, 41); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: normal;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(29, 33, 41); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: normal;\">Dinner will be served at 10.00pm followed by some travel stories and fun games.</span><br style=\"color: rgb(29, 33, 41); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: normal;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(29, 33, 41); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: normal;\">The night stay will be at our local guide village house.</span><br style=\"color: rgb(29, 33, 41); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: normal;\"><br style=\"color: rgb(29, 33, 41); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: normal;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(29, 33, 41); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: normal;\">Day 2 (Sunday) :</span><br style=\"color: rgb(29, 33, 41); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: normal;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(29, 33, 41); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: normal;\">Wake up call will be at 4.00am. The early we start the better it is.</span><br style=\"color: rgb(29, 33, 41); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: normal;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(29, 33, 41); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: normal;\">After having breakfast we will start at 5.00am with the day long trek. On an average it takes 3hr to reach till the top.&nbsp;</span><br style=\"color: rgb(29, 33, 41); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: normal;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(29, 33, 41); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: normal;\">A good 30 min will be spend at the summit before starting our journey back to the village. The return journey takes another 2-2.5hr. Lunch will be ready on reaching the village for all our hungry souls.</span><br style=\"color: rgb(29, 33, 41); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: normal;\"><br style=\"color: rgb(29, 33, 41); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: normal;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(29, 33, 41); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: normal;\">After lunch and a quick rest of 30min the return journey to Kasara begins from where the people can go back to their destination.</span><br style=\"color: rgb(29, 33, 41); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: normal;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(29, 33, 41); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: normal;\">We will reach back to Kasara station by 5pm.</span><br style=\"color: rgb(29, 33, 41); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: normal;\"><br style=\"color: rgb(29, 33, 41); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: normal;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(29, 33, 41); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: normal;\">Cost: Rs.1650/- (inclusive of gst)</span><br style=\"color: rgb(29, 33, 41); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: normal;\"><br style=\"color: rgb(29, 33, 41); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: normal;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(29, 33, 41); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: normal;\"><b>Inclusions:</b></span><br style=\"color: rgb(29, 33, 41); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: normal;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(29, 33, 41); font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: normal;\">. Travelling from Kasara to Kasara in jeep.</span><br style=\"color: rgb(29, 33